summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Homecroft Addition to the City of Seattle; Boulevard Park Addition; vacated Maynard Avenue South; Diagonal Avenue South; Morningside Acre Tracts; Queen Anne Park Addition to the City of Seattle; vacated Jesse Avenue West; D.T. Denny's Plan of North Seattle Addition; and vacated 39th Place Northeast, as described below and placing said easement under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
